What do you guys think about combining CS and psychology? 

I have 6 years experience of in programming, now I'm passionate about AI. But also, in my free time, I like to study psychology. I've taken both AP CS and AP Psychology classes.
I'm using the second brain method to combine my notes and thoughts about psychology and CS and find some connections and relationships. I've personally found some really interesting and fascinating things, and in the future, I'd like to make some researches by using all the tracks that I've done.
